                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971206-48-off257 t17971206-48-cd258"></join>, a cloth great coat, value 10s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17971206-48-victim459" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Daniel
               <interp inst="t17971206-48-victim459" type="surname" value="Daniel"></interp>
